   /* --- MAIN CONTROLLING STYLES --- */
html, body, div, span, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p, a, dl, dt, dd, ol, ul, li, form, label, table, tbody, tfoot, thead, tr, th, td {margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;outline: 0;font-weight: inherit;font-style: inherit;font-size: 93%;font-family: inherit;}

body {

a, a:hover, a:visited {

}

#centeredpage {
	margin:0 auto;

}

.logo {

.content h1 {

}

.formfield label {

}

.formfield input {

}

	margin-top: 2px;
}

	color: #000000;
}

	font-size: 1.0em;
	line-height: 12px;
	margin-bottom: 15px;
}

	font-size: 1.0em;
    text-decoration: underline;

p.terms {

.showTOC {

p.loginmessage {

}
